{"about_the_game":"<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>The operation of this game is very unique. It is recommended to watch the How-to- play video at the top of the page before trying it.</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a minesweeper game from a third-person perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Marking all mines is the task of each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214770/extras/01-minesweeper.gif?t=1730001223\" />Minefields may be covered by obstacles and can be cleared by blasting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214770/extras/02-bomb.gif?t=1730001223\" />In the levels, you will encounter guards who prevent your action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have a wealth of skills to fight them,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hand-to-hand combat is your basic skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214770/extras/03-kick.gif?t=1730001223\" />There are many more skills that you are welcome to experience for yourself once you enter the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, we provide the first 6 levels of the game for you to experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can use the experience points you earn in the game to strengthen your skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The parlay record will be displayed so that you can try it again and again.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214770/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730001223","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214770/page.bg.jpg?t=1730001223","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214770/48da02b7